Levitt Says Steve Jobs Disinvited Him From Board (Audio)

-- B y  
-- 
2011-10-06T16:07:08Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-06/levitt-says-steve-jobs-disinvited-him-from-board-audio-.html
Arthur Levitt , a former chairman of 
the SEC, says Apple founder Steve Jobs invited then disinvited 
him to join the company board.  Levitt talks with Bloomberg's 
Ken Prewitt and Pimm Fox on Bloomberg Radio's "Bloomberg 
Surveillance."     (Source: Bloomberg)  Running time 08:47
 